title: HOUR 3- Sep 21, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Sep 21, 2020
description:
Dan Patrick talks about all the injuries to key players in the NFL on Sunday. Dan says the LA Chargers have a real question on their hands at quarterback. Dan says the Chargers need to weigh out what is at stake and probably start Justin Herbert now.
